title: Kristina Rose Megapack
description:
Kristina Rose (born April 14, 1984) is the stage name of an American pornographic actress

At age 18, Rose first worked for an adult website doing customer service. When the company moved, she was laid off, and the only companies that responded to her resume were adult-related companies. She became an assistant for a photographer who encouraged her to model, but she did not start modeling until she was 23 years-old.

Rose began appearing in adult films around 2007, and she has since appeared in over 490 movies. She performed her first anal sex scene in Elegant Angel's 2008 movie Kristina Rose: Dirty Girl and her first DP in the 2009 movie Kristina Rose Is Slutwoman.
